&lt;/ul&gt;</description><link>http://colamundo.tumblr.com/post/1170928593</link><guid>http://colamundo.tumblr.com/post/1170928593</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Sep 2010 23:11:17 -0400</pubDate><category>mídia analógica</category><category>áudio</category><category>rádio gazeta</category></item><item><title>"Toda reforma interior e toda mudança para melhor dependem exclusivamente da aplicação do nosso..."</title><description>“Toda reforma interior e toda mudança para melhor dependem exclusivamente da aplicação do nosso próprio esforço”&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; - &lt;em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Immanuel Kant&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;</description><link>http://colamundo.tumblr.com/post/1170912949</link><guid>http://colamundo.tumblr.com/post/1170912949</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Sep 2010 23:08:28 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>Indivíduo e Cultura:Perspectivas da Antropologia Contemporânea</title><description>&lt;a href="http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?oe=UTF-8&amp;hl=pt&amp;q=cache:5lhJm0Un_F4J:www.cchla.ufpb.br/caos/maykandreele.pdf"&gt;Indivíduo e Cultura:Perspectivas da Antropologia Contemporânea&lt;/a&gt;</description><link>http://colamundo.tumblr.com/post/1170907296</link><guid>http://colamundo.tumblr.com/post/1170907296</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Sep 2010 23:07:29 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>Piores vexames do google // There’s No Success Like Failure: Google’s Biggest Product Flops</title><description>&lt;a href="http://techcrunch.com/2010/08/18/is-google-me-nex/"&gt;Piores vexames do google // There’s No Success Like Failure: Google’s Biggest Product Flops&lt;/a&gt;</description><link>http://colamundo.tumblr.com/post/1170899820</link><guid>http://colamundo.tumblr.com/post/1170899820</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Sep 2010 23:06:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>Bateria Humana / The human battery: turning body heat into electric power</title><description>&lt;a href="http://www.gizmag.com/go/7731/"&gt;Bateria Humana / The human battery: turning body hea